## Summary

This documentation covers the Amplitude Experiment iOS SDK for client-side feature flag evaluation, including installation via CocoaPods/SPM, initialization with Amplitude Analytics integration, remote/local evaluation through fetch() and start() methods, variant access with automatic exposure tracking, and provider interfaces for custom user management and analytics integration.

